items.badge_name: Wake Up and Smell The Coffee! (Level 12)
items.badge_description: Coffee has long been a flavor counterpart for stouts and porters, which means Coffee's not just for breakfast anymore. That's 60 different beers with the style of Porter - Coffee, Porter - Imperial / Double Coffee, Stout - Imperial / Double Coffee, or Stout - Coffee. Try 5 more for Level 13!

Porters and Stouts are rich with both history and flavor. Roasty, dark, and delicious, these two styles helped start it all. That’s 110 different beers with the style of Porter or Stout. Try 5 more for Level 23!
Happy Untappd anniversary to you! Thanks for sticking around and drinking socially with us. Cheers! That's 6 years on Untappd!

Want to enjoy a day of brews, but need to keep your wits sharp? There are plenty of delicious brews under 5% for you to sip on throughout the day. That's 80 different beers with an ABV of 5% and lower. Try 5 more for Level 17!

items.badge_name: Beyond a Shadow of a Stout (Level 2)
items.badge_description: We all love Stouts, and now we have a dedicated badge to celebrate your dedication to these dark, top-fermented beer in multiple variations, like Oatmeal, Milk and more! Which one will you start with? That's 10 different beers with the style of Stout. Try 5 more for Level 3!

items.checkin_comment: Is it blood? Not but it’s a bloody good stout. Tastes like a cold brew juice smoothie. Great refresher after a day on the slopes 🤙

items.badge_description:
Hoppy International Beer Day!

Beer serves as the common thread that links us worldwide, possessing the ability to bring people together in a unique way.

Beer has played a significant role in shaping countless of our most cherished memories. And if there’s one thing we’ve learned along the way, beer is best when shared with others.
